attributes.Long form description: The student is disassembling a rolling cart. They start by taking off the wheels, then flipping the cart over to work on the underside. They remove the screws and brackets holding the tray in place, then take off the tray. They repeat this process for the middle and bottom tray. Finally, they unscrew the legs of the cart base.
